head.note:
In English and German;
                                    German text not printed. Ratification advised by the Senate,
                                    August 24, 1935; ratified by the President, August 28, 1935;
                                    ratified by Germany, September 28, 1935; ratifications exchanged
                                    at Berlin, October 7, 1935; proclaimed by the President, October
                                    25, 1935.
